|Footman Halberd=3;spear24;Spear;Common;metal;130;1;1625;1;20;25;18;23;;;;;;;;;;;;;;4;;;;;8;;;;;;16;;;;30;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;aldor;23;;A halberd is beloved by the Aldorian infantry for its versatility. Being able to use your weapon for both slashing and thrusting attacks is a valuable asset on the battlefield.
 
