|Eederax=4;gaxe11;Two-handed Axe;Common;metal;155;1;3625;1;40;25;;29;;;;;;;;;;;;;;7;12;;;;10;;;;10;;;;;;30;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;aldor;29;;When the Aldorian army was routed by the Nistrian cavalry at the battle of Thorny Hill, the Eeders militia took the humiliating defeat to heart and started attaching special anti-cavalry hooks to their axes.
 
