|Aldwynn Crossbow=4;crossbow05;Crossbow;Common;wood;90;1;3150;7;10;25;;;26;;;;;;;;;;;;-24;;;;;;-12;;;;;15;25;;;;10;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;;1;aldor;26;;A while ago, His Lordship Brodwyn der Razen made it his personal mission to fit his soldiers with crossbows of this design. His success inspired some other prominent Council commanders to eventually do the same.
 
